## Introduction:

Skincare products have gained popularity to help alleviate skin problems recently, such as skin problems namely acne, sunburn, and pimple brought by the humid weather. However, many people have difficulty choosing the appropriate skincare products for their skin type. The purpose of this project is to conduct an analysis based on a survey in terms of several factors such as skin condition, product selection and skincare goals, and build a model to predict the purchasing capability on skincare products in the future.

## Beneficiary of the product:

Young segment (teenagers) or adult woman but not limited to male as well.


