Conclusion
========================================================
<li> The Random Forest model obtained a high accuracy in predicting the consumption level of customers. Thus, it can assist in product selection, which means we can use the survey to group the customers and forecast their purchasing capability in the future. However, this app also has some limitations as results generated based on a small-size dataset. Therefore, continuously improvements need to be implemented in the face of challenges and issues.
